FREETOUR.com Liabilities & Customer Assumption of risk
Because Freetour.com is a platform that makes it easy to book tours with independent tour operators, therefore Freetour.com does not own, operate or provide tours.
And also considering that when booking a tour, you enter into a contract directly with the tour operator, and not with Freetour.com, our sites or services, and it is the tour provider that is solely responsible for the performance of this contract on their part and for providing you with travel services in accordance with booked or an alternative that satisfies you, if applicable.
In connection with the foregoing, FREETOUR.com, including but not limited to, is not responsible for:
Cancellation of the tour by the tour provider at any time before the start of the tour, including with or without indicating the reasons for such cancellation;
Non-arrival of the tour operator (the tour provider) at the agreed place of the start of the tour, including with or without indicating the reasons for such non-arrival;
Change by the tour operator of the time and / or place of the tour, including with or without indicating the reasons for such changes;
Additional costs of the User related to the organization of travel (including, but not limited to: the cost of the train, accommodation, etc.), part of which was supposed to be a tour that was canceled by the tour operator;
Lack of telephone or any other communication with the tour operator, for reasons depending on it or regardless of this, due to which communication between you and the tour operator was or is impossible;
Misunderstanding that arose when you communicated with the tour operator, both when booking a tour and during the tour itself;
Disagreements between you and the tour operator regarding, including, but not limited to: the itinerary of the tour; tour descriptions; any comments and advice that were voiced by the tour operator; difference in political and religious views with the tour operator, etc.;
Acceptance of risk and responsibility by the User
You acknowledge that Freetour.com is a platform that makes it easy to book tours with independent tour operators, and therefore Freetour.com is not responsible for the words and actions of the tour operator, and that any statements of providers, their political, religious and other views and preferences do not represent the views of FREETOUR.com.
Thus, you assume the risks associated with:
Personal communication with providers when booking a tour or related to such booking (including by telephone, SMS or otherwise), which may lead to inappropriate comments or misconduct on the part of the provider. FREETOUR.com recommends that in this case immediately stop communication with the provider and inform the FREETOUR.com support service;
Cancellation of the tour booking by the provider and / or cancellation of the tour directly at the meeting point (provider's no-show). In this case, the User assumes the risk of dealing with the cancellation of the tour on his own. In case of cancellation by the tour operator of a paid reservation, such refusal / cancellation always entails a full refund to the User.
Dissatisfaction with the content of the tour or the provider (guide). Such dissatisfaction with the content of the tour or the tour operator (guide) is not a reason for non-payment for this tour and / or for a refund for such a tour.
Be exposed to any personal views and points of view of the tour operator during the tour, including, but not exclusively: stories about the personal life and activities of the tour operator, his personal religious, political preferences and views. Any statements of providers, their political, religious and other views and preferences do not reflect the views of FREETOUR.com.
